The cold wind blew. 
Conor was awaken by the swoosh of wind that banged against the windows.
He saw the most monstrous person in the world. It was Aeon Lee. Conor shivered at the sight of Aeon Lee Zi Lin, the person who everyone feared, the person who thought Bill Gates was the inventor of Apple, the person who doesnt even know what porn is. 
Aeon wore transparent spectacles , the most powerful one in the world. 
everyone feared Aeons lack of knowledge and brainless mind who doesnt know anything. 
